80 partners from 11 districts in 8 provinces/ cities have competed for the title of Barista Championship. The Final Round took place on September 6, 2023 at the Starbucks Vietnam Office among the top 6 most talented partners from 3 cities: HCMC, Hai Phong and Hanoi.

All 6 baristas have competed in 3 categories in 20 minutes, including Pour-over, Latte Art, Signature Beverage to show their passion, skills and knowledge of coffee.
And the 2023 #Champion is Luong Gia Khanh from Starbucks Reserve Han Thuyen and the runner-up is Nguyen Dai Nguyen from Starbucks Van Hanh Mall.
